        <h5>Cocktails App</h5>
        <p>This cocktails app is a collaborative project between a group of CoderAcademy students that wanted an extra-curricular project to contribute to outside of class.  This is also a Ruby terminal app at this stage and will provide the user with a list of cocktails that can be made with the specific alcohols that you enter/ have on hand, including recipes for those cocktails.  Contributors - <a href="https://github.com/prfraser" target="_blank">Philip Fraser</a>, <a href="https://github.com/DeadFred121" target="_blank">Fred Cliff</a>, <a href="https://github.com/FilipMaslovaric" target="_blank">Filip Masolvaric</a> and myself.</p>
      </div>
